:"2020-12-23T10:39:44.000Z","msg":"綜援似d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"515075c7a670829cb28d5ed4bd11115605d1d798","tid":2337445,"uid":29093,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T11:09:06.000Z","msg":"貧窮綫分界<br />\n人數 每月收入（港元）<br />\n一人 4,000<br />\n二人 9,800<br />\n三人 15,000<br />\n四人 19,900<br />\n五人 20,300<br />\n六人及以上 22,500<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\">都幾痴線   香港真係一個地獄嚟</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n問：香港是如何界定貧窮綫？<br />\n<br />\n答：香港的貧窮綫計算方法是用「相對貧窮」的概念，按住戶人數來劃分，<span class=\"red\">以全港每月住戶的收入中位數（政策介入前，即扣除社會福利的收入）的50%作為貧窮綫</span>。每戶家庭收入少於以下貧窮綫的水平，即屬貧窮人口。這個貧窮綫的分界會因應全港市民收入水平不斷浮動。"},{"pid":"c99971aa599392f6f7939c81408a133b2f1a6656","tid":2337445,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T11:09:44.000Z","msg":"149+1<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"798afbe6079d9ca66316813b100cbe8f000863a9","tid":2337445,"uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"08408576365c13b752ce1f5130ace281dc73a732","tid":2337445,"uid":275218,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T09:52:43.000Z","msg":"移民再走一堆<br />\n大陸再落黎一堆<br />\n好快破200萬"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T11:10:02.000Z","msg":"食窮港共<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}